    "Full implementation details are available in our repository [46].",
    "C. Evaluation MeasuresWe report runtime, accuracy via MAE, and calibration via calibration curves and ECE.",
    "Let S = {(i, j): M ij = 0} denote masked cells.",
    "With ground truth x ij and imputed mean xij,M AE = 1 |S| (i,j)∈S x ij -xij.Lower MAE indicates better reconstruction on the same masked set.",
